These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, metal
1. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | teacher | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | techno  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: mouse, frog
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, train
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | frog   | mouse      |
| Transport   | roller | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, folk
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard
1. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | disco    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, scientific
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, country
1. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | trance | country |

